Just taking a stab that hch means,
config BINFMT_COMPAT_ELF
	def_bool n
	depends on 64BIT
and then in arch/powerpc/Kconfig
config COMPAT
	bool
	default y if PPC64
	select BINFMT_COMPAT_ELF
or somesuch.
